%% Zaude session lifecycle. Render with any Mermaid-compatible renderer.

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as You
    participant CC as Claude Code
    participant H as SessionStart hook
    participant V as Vault
    participant M as Memory
    participant R as Remote (GitHub)

    U->>CC: Open Claude Code session
    CC->>H: fire SessionStart
    H->>V: read CLAUDE.md, current-state, decisions,<br/>open-questions, spec, architecture,<br/>last 3 session logs
    H->>V: read 03-patterns/*.md
    H->>M: read every memory file
    H->>CC: inject as additionalContext

    U->>CC: /start
    CC->>U: Report:<br/>• last session summary<br/>• in-flight work<br/>• blocking issues<br/>• active memory rules<br/>• next concrete action

    U->>CC: /build <feature>
    Note over CC: plan → design → implement<br/>→ code-reviewer<br/>→ architect-review (REVIEW)<br/>→ security-auditor (if applicable)
    CC->>U: Findings by severity

    U->>CC: /ship (if review passed)
    Note over CC: commit, push to project remote,<br/>update current-state.md,<br/>append session log + decisions
    CC->>R: push project + vault

    U->>CC: /wrap
    Note over CC: final code review,<br/>vault update, memory sweep,<br/>credential rotation list
    CC->>R: push vault + claude-config
